21
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:47,599
Mom.

22
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:48,959
Mom.

23
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,519
Mom.

24
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,920
I was tricked by that Tang Yan.

25
