83
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:08,240
After suffering some hardships, she finally grew up.

84
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,680
Wang Yingzhu returned to the workplace and gained confidence.

85
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,039
She also found her true self.

86
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:17,279
