247
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,879
Zhen Zhen has a boyfriend?

248
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,240
Young people these days...

249
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,679
I don't know what they...

250
00:09:12,679 --> 00:09:13,399
I know.

251
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,440
Anyway...

252
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,639
